data.description: UNZONED – 5 acres with COMMERCIAL POTENTIAL, Southeast Corner of Beach Express and CO RD 36. Fantastic location for retail or gas-convenience store. Car count is 19800 + on The Beach Express. Southern Alabama’s Coastal Region is continually expanding. Large new home subdivision is going in across the street on CO RD 36. Turn lanes in place on CO RD 36, and available directly off The Beach Express. This sale includes two parcels, #213402 and #205453. Call for more information. Mobile home on property is at no value.  All information provided is deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buyer or buyer’s agent to verify all information.
